import React from 'react'

import PokemonMainContent from './PokemonMainContent'
import PokemonSideBar from './PokemonSideBar'
import Col from '../../../components/grid/Col'
import Container from '../../../components/sctructure/Container'
import FullPageTemplate from '../../../components/templates/FullPageTemplate'
import Grid from '../../../components/grid/Grid'
import ShowPokemonPageHeader from './ShowPokemonPageHeader'

const ShowPokemonPage = ({match: {params}}) => (
  <FullPageTemplate>
    <ShowPokemonPageHeader />
    <Container>
      <Grid largeGutter>
        <Col flex={0} largeGutter>
          <PokemonSideBar />
        </Col>

        <Col largeGutter>
          <PokemonMainContent />
        </Col>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  </FullPageTemplate>
)

export default ShowPokemonPage
